{"tid":1273253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(急)各位義士最後一步做錯左","createTime":"2019-07-01T13:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T14:08:27.000Z","uid":119409,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e88bf9f0caf1be74b62bb99b21e212db4899605","tid":1273253,"uid":119409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"大家今日做得好好<br />\n但最後一步係咪做錯左<br />\n今日目的最緊要係搏到<br />\n全香港人同外國最大正面回響<br />\n唔應該掛港英旗同塗鴉區輝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解唔用黑布擋住就算<br />\n然後將議事堂變為靈堂<br />\n紀念義士呢<br />\n老實講 就算西方國家<br />\n大部份人都唔會同意破壞自己國家旗<br />\n同掛其他國家旗<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我自己睇法<br />\n但尊重大家"},{"pid":"69bbe8347b91f1d4e57a897482c8c9d88a2027cd","tid":1273253,"uid":131084,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:56:27.000Z","msg":"我既國家係香港<br />\n唔係中國 更加唔係香港特別行政區"},{"pid":"9dab659e13844564b57292c401e0fa9e0d03cc9f","tid":1273253,"uid":119409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"就算大家唔同意我所講<br />\n可唔可以幫義士悼念一下?"},{"pid":"f27fe2260cc37f866bfbe13b6106f0d34cdf993c","tid":1273253,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:58:04.000Z","msg":"香港旗係本地旗"},{"pid":"d8644fb5b830815febcdf3df1f12f6a9bf15d47c","tid":1273253,"uid":119409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}